      only go so far. If a post has a slider or a plot you can click, it's
      because the idea is easier to feel than to describe.
    </p>
    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
